              },
              "blocks": {
                "accordion_row_dkWQVy": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Key Benefits",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_fTwpHY": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>CLEAR - </strong>Supports your body's natural breakdown of acetaldehyde, the toxic alcohol byproduct that causes rough mornings.</p><p><strong>PROTECT - </strong>Promotes liver health and supports your natural detox pathways during alcohol metabolism.</p><p><strong>RESTORE - </strong>Replenishes the glutathione, B vitamins, and antioxidants that alcohol directly depletes overnight.</p><p><strong>SHOW UP - </strong>So you wake up feeling balanced, clear, and ready for whatever the day holds.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "rte",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                        "font_size": "1rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "text_color": "",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_fTwpHY"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_FCBcPE": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How it Works",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_CThjz6": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>When you drink, your liver converts alcohol into acetaldehyde - a highly toxic compound responsible for nausea, flushing, headaches, and hangovers.</p><p>ALDH2 enzymes further break down acetaldehyde into harmless acetate. But this process takes time - around one drink per hour - and is even slower for those with an ALDH2 deficiency (~50% of East Asians). This allows acetaldehyde to build up to dangerous levels.</p><p>Kanbae supercharges ALDH activity, boosts antioxidants, and replenishes nutrients to help clear acetaldehyde faster while protecting your liver.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "rte",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                        "font_size": "1rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "text_color": "",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_CThjz6"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_QYJKRF": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "When to Take",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_xHbFMc": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>Before: </strong>Take 2 capsules (1 sachet) 15-30 minutes before drinking, as they take time to break down in your stomach.</p><p><strong>After: </strong>If you’ve had a heavy session, you can take up to 2 more capsules after your last drink.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "rte",
