                  "blocks": {
                    "text_AzA8yb": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Our products are formulated in-house by Singapore Health Sciences Authority (HSA) accredited experts.</p><p>DrinkAid is the only anti-hangover brand to have been clinically tested for efficacy.</p><p>Our products are made in and shipped from Singapore, third-party tested, and manufactured in a GMP-certified facility.</p>",
